overview: Being a personal assistant means attending to every need that the boss may have, and the girls in this film have been hand selected through weeks of auditions and trials. The dudes don't want just any girl for, "Personal Assistant," because the asses in question must be used to getting penetrated by huge cocks, because these bosses get a lot of work done throughout the day and need a tight warm place to release a day's worth of tension, sometimes even twice a day!
title: Personal Assistants 1
